1936;;The Gay Desperado;;American;;Rouben Mamoulian;;Ida Lupino, Leo Carrillo;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Gay_Desperado;;Chivo, a singer who works in a movie theater providing live entertainment, is and apprehended by a music-loving Mexican bandit Braganza who wants to make Chivo part of his band. Braganza, who admires American gangsters, also kidnaps Jane and her rich boyfriend, Bill. to become more like the American movie gangsters he admires.